title: Just reporting a small typo
body:
Don't mind me, I'm just passing by, reporting a small typo in [Twilight of the Gods](https://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_GB/story/twilight-of-the-gods/). There's a darkin named Enakai who's being called "Enekai" twice. It's no big deal but oh well!

Just got a picture as a proof. Enakai is mentioned 11 times while Enekai only 2, so I'm guessing Enekai is the wrong one :p

replies.body:
{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}} 
D'oh! Thanks for the heads up!
